{"title":"MET update the Manta MIPS Road helmet with smokin’ hot aero design","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/01/met-update-the-manta-mips-road-helmet-with-smokin-hot-aero-design/","date":1614585627000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>The new <span>MET</span> Manta MIPS draws on the natural geometry of its predecessor as a guide but is now more aerodynamic than ever with sharper looks and enhanced safety tech. The new lid puts a big focus on ventilation too, packing MET’s proprietary NACA vent system. Let’s check out the finer details.</p><h3>MET Manta MIPS Aero Road Helmet</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-more-aero.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-more-aero.jpg\" alt=\"new met manta mips more aerodynamic rear shape\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-more-aero.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-more-aero-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-more-aero-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-more-aero-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-more-aero-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-more-aero-696x522.jpg 696w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-more-aero-1068x801.jpg 1068w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-more-aero-560x420.jpg 560w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-more-aero-80x60.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-more-aero-265x198.jpg 265w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\"></a></p><p>That last iteration of the MET Manta was one designed specifically for the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2016/05/16/met-slips-special-edition-cvndsh-manta-aero-lid/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Manx Missile</a>, Mark Cavendish. For 2021, the shape gets a significant update. Following wind tunnel tests at the Newton Laboratory of Milan, this road lid gets a lower and tube-shaped profile at the rear, now more aerodynamic than ever. <em>And</em> it’s safer.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-safety-brain-protection-system.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-safety-brain-protection-system.jpg\" alt=\"met helmets manta mips-c2 rotational impact protection system\" width=\"1200\" height=\"754\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-safety-brain-protection-system.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-safety-brain-protection-system-297x187.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-safety-brain-protection-system-800x503.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-safety-brain-protection-system-120x75.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-safety-brain-protection-system-768x483.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-safety-brain-protection-system-696x437.jpg 696w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-safety-brain-protection-system-1068x671.jpg 1068w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-safety-brain-protection-system-668x420.jpg 668w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\"></a></p><p>Safety technology comes in the form of MIPS-C2 rotational impact protection system. Now a common safety feature on many road and mountain bike helmets alike, the MIPS liner permits 10-15mm of movement upon impact. That dissociates rotational forces experienced by the helmet from movement of the rider’s head, helping to prevent concussion injury.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-fidlock-magnetic-buckle.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-fidlock-magnetic-buckle.jpg\" alt=\"met manta mips road aero helmet\" width=\"1200\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-fidlock-magnetic-buckle.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-fidlock-magnetic-buckle-297x93.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-fidlock-magnetic-buckle-800x251.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-fidlock-magnetic-buckle-120x38.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-fidlock-magnetic-buckle-768x241.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-fidlock-magnetic-buckle-696x218.jpg 696w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-helmets-Manta-Mips-product-detail-fidlock-magnetic-buckle-1068x335.jpg 1068w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\"></a></p><p>With safety and aerodynamics taken care of, the new MET Manta MIPS also packs in everything you might expect from a high-end road helmet; a magnetic Fidlock closure said to effectively reduce triathlon transition times, 15 vents with internal air flow designed to minimize drag, and two ports for docking sunglasses.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet.jpg\" alt=\"met manta mips road cycling helmet front view\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-696x522.jpg 696w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-1068x801.jpg 1068w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-560x420.jpg 560w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-80x60.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-265x198.jpg 265w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\"></a></p><p>With internals taken from the MET Trenta 3K Carbon, the Manta MIPS gets a 360° head belt meant to result in no pressure points on the skull. The fitment system can be adjusted vertically to suit different head shapes, while adjustable cam dividers ensure all riders can position the divider correctly; directly underneath the ear lobe.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-5.jpg\" alt=\"met manta mips aero road helmet top view\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-5.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-5-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-5-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-5-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-5-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-5-696x522.jpg 696w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-5-1068x801.jpg 1068w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-5-560x420.jpg 560w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-5-80x60.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-5-265x198.jpg 265w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\"></a></p><h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-met-Manta-Mips-road-cyclign-helmets-all-colors.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-met-Manta-Mips-road-cyclign-helmets-all-colors.jpg\" alt=\"2021 met manta mips colorways\" width=\"1200\" height=\"625\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-met-Manta-Mips-road-cyclign-helmets-all-colors.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-met-Manta-Mips-road-cyclign-helmets-all-colors-297x155.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-met-Manta-Mips-road-cyclign-helmets-all-colors-800x417.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-met-Manta-Mips-road-cyclign-helmets-all-colors-120x63.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-met-Manta-Mips-road-cyclign-helmets-all-colors-768x400.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-met-Manta-Mips-road-cyclign-helmets-all-colors-696x363.jpg 696w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-met-Manta-Mips-road-cyclign-helmets-all-colors-1068x556.jpg 1068w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-met-Manta-Mips-road-cyclign-helmets-all-colors-806x420.jpg 806w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\"></a></p><p>Pick up the new MET Manta MIPS aero road helmet for 250€ / £220 / US$300 / CAD$380 / AUS$400 in one of six colorways.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-7.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-7.jpg\" alt=\"met manta mips road cycling helmet aerodynamic rear view\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-7.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-7-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-7-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-7-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-7-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-7-696x522.jpg 696w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-7-1068x801.jpg 1068w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-7-560x420.jpg 560w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-7-80x60.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/met-manta-mips-road-cycling-helmet-7-265x198.jpg 265w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\"></a></p><p><strong>• </strong>Claimed weight